data.title: Prime Video: Go West
data.meta_description: The original cast of the hit sketch comedy show, Studio C, has made a movie! Go West tells the tale of a ragtag handcart company traveling the US Oregon Trail during the 1800s- but, like, in a fun way. Along the way, they meet a crazy cast of characters, cross exotic states (like Nebraska), and risk terrible danger (like Nebraska). Watch this movie, you may die of laughter. Or Dysentery.
